text: Seen is a district in the city of Winterthur in Switzerland. It is District number 3. The district has these quarters: Waser, Büelwiesen, Waldegg, Ganzenbühl, Sonnenberg, Ricketwil, Oberseen, Gotzenwil, Eidberg, Iberg and Sennhof. Until 1922 it was a municipality on its own. Then it became part of Winterthur. Category:Former municipalities of Zürich Category:Winterthur
title: Seen (Winterthur)
